window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Half-dwarven craftswoman, enchanter, and hammer-wielder Matti Puletasi has achieved most of her goals, and even found the love of the handsome elf assassin Sarrlevi.</p> <p>Unfortunately, there’s still a bounty on her head. That makes it hard to return to a normal life, start a family, or even visit the Coffee Dragon without being shot at.</p> <p>Worse, one of Sarrlevi’s old elven lovers shows up, hinting of changes back home that mean his exile could be lifted and his nobility returned—if only he’ll dance to her tune.</p> <p>Matti knows Sarrlevi loves her, but worries she’ll be tempted. A chance to return home and be a hero instead of an outcast—who wouldn’t long for that?</p>"; 
